_:N65beadec05a94f7ea5b1a5eb37e5f55f <http://schema.org/name> "The Rt Hon Ellie Reeves KC MP" .
_:N65beadec05a94f7ea5b1a5eb37e5f55f <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Ellie Reeves was appointed as Solicitor General on 6 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>She was previously Minister without Portfolio at the Cabinet Office from 6 July 2024 to 6 September 2025. She was elected as the MP for Lewisham West and East Dulwich in 2024 and was previously the MP for Lewisham West and Penge from 2017.</p>\n" .
